## Code Generation

### Full CRUD Resource

```bash
swap g r Product --fields "Name:string Price:decimal InStock:bool:f"
```

Generates:
- `Models/Product.cs`
- `Controllers/ProductsController.cs`
- `Views/Products/Index.cshtml`
- `Views/Products/_ProductList.cshtml`
- `Views/Products/_ProductForm.cshtml`
- `Views/Products/_ProductItem.cshtml`
- Event chain in `Events/SwapEventChains.cs`

### Model Only

```bash
swap g m Category --fields "Name:string Slug:string Description:string?"
```

### Controller Only

```bash
swap g c Orders --fields "OrderNumber:string Total:decimal"
```

**Field syntax:**
- `Name:string` — Required string
- `Description:string?` — Optional string
- `Price:decimal` — Required decimal
- `InStock:bool:f` — Boolean with `false` default

