## Testing

### Run All Tests

```bash
dotnet test
```

### Run Specific Test

```bash
dotnet test --filter "FullyQualifiedName~TodoFlowTests"
```

### Watch Mode

```bash
dotnet watch test
```

### Writing HTMX Integration Tests

```csharp
public class MyFeatureTests : IClassFixture<HtmxTestFixture<Program>>
{
    private readonly HtmxTestClient<Program> _client;
    
    public MyFeatureTests(HtmxTestFixture<Program> fixture)
    {
        _client = fixture.Client;
    }
    
    [Fact]
    public async Task Should_Create_And_Display_Item()
    {
        // Arrange
        var formData = new Dictionary<string, string>
        {
            ["title"] = "Test Item"
        };
        
        // Act
        var response = await _client.HtmxPostAsync("/Home/AddTodo", formData);
        
        // Assert
        response.AssertSuccess();
        response.AssertHasSwapEvent("entity.created:todo");
        
        var list = await _client.HtmxGetAsync("/Home/TodoList");
        await list.AssertContainsAsync("Test Item");
    }
}
```

**Available assertions:**
- `AssertSuccess()` — 2xx status code
- `AssertPartialViewAsync()` — Response is a partial view
- `AssertContainsAsync(text)` — HTML contains text
- `AssertHasSwapEvent(name)` — Event was fired
- `AssertHxRedirect(url)` — HTMX redirect header present

