      "args": [],
      "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}/src",
      "env": {
        "ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT": "Development"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

### Visual Studio 2022

1. Open `{{ProjectName}}.sln`
2. Set startup project to `src/{{ProjectName}}.csproj`
3. Press F5 to run with debugging

### JetBrains Rider

1. Open `{{ProjectName}}.sln`
2. Right-click `Program.cs` → Run
3. Breakpoints work automatically

